# CORE DEVELOPMENT RULES

## AI Behavior Rules
- Always generate production-ready Laravel code.
- Never output pseudo-code unless explicitly requested.
- Prefer clean architecture over quick hacks.
- Follow SOLID principles strictly.

## Architecture Enforcement
- Controllers = request handling only
- Services = business logic
- Actions = single responsibility tasks
- Repositories = database abstraction (when needed)

## Strict Rules
- No raw DB queries in controllers
- No logic inside Blade views
- No validation inside controllers